<template>
     <v-text-field
         class="textsize"
            color="#264F7E"
            v-model="fname"
            :rules="reqRules"
            :label="value"
            dir="rtl"
            required
          ></v-text-field>
</template>
<script>
export default {
     data: () => ({
      valid: false,
      default: '',
      reqRules: [
        v => !!v || '',
      ],
    }),
    props:{
        value: {
            required: true
        }
    }
}
</script>
<style>
.theme--light.v-input {
     color:  #e0e9f0 !important;
}
.v-input__slot{
    text-align: right !important;
    direction: rtl !important;
    border-bottom: 2px solid #e3eaf0 !important;
    font-size: 16px !important;
}
.theme--light.v-text-field > .v-input__control > .v-input__slot:before {
    border-width: 1px !important;
}
.v-label {
    position: absolute !important;
    bottom: 4px !important;
    color: #a1b5c5 !important;
}

</style>
